How to unlock Dell 1F66,6FF1,1F5A or 3A5B

If you have a Dell notebook with ServiceTag: 1FF6,  6FF1, 1F5A or 3A5B

our site will allow you remove password from  BIOS or HDD.

You must only specify for us your ServiceTag which you can see as soon as you turn on your notebook. We will do for you the hardest part – by removing the password. 

How to remove password? Here’s an instruction:

  1. When you turn on your notebook, you should wait for the screen with a password.
    Here you will find ServiceTag. It’s a string of seven digits, then dash and at the end: 1FF6, 6FF1, 1F5A or 3A5B, for example, 1234567-1F66
  1. In the figure below CZ224X1-1F66   is the service Tag

  1. Then go to the Dell password page below and enter your service tag there  and click send button to send the information
    After that click button buy now with paypal pressing payments and do all payment process,  we will send the password to your e-mail.

How to enter the password:

  • If the keyboard type on your notebook is German ( QWERTZ ) or French ( AZERTY ), connect a USB keyboard with QWERTY type
  • Enter the password slowly. Pay attention to big and small letters. Rewrite the password identically, as we sent you on e–mail.
  • In the case of the password protected on the BIOS : After entering your password, press the left Ctrl key and continue holding it, press Enter twice
    If the password on the BIOS SETTINGS only: press Enter
  • If you filed for the first time to remove the password, restart your computer and try again.

content.rendered:
How to unlock Acer, Gateway, PackardBell  bios Password

If you have an Acer, Gateway, PackardBell 10 Decimal digits example 2039837875, we will give you the possibility for you to remove the password from  BIOS

  • Power on your laptop and wait for the password screen
  • Enter the wrong password three times
  • You will receive the Key from which the password can be calculated.

  • Please Type your Key example see picture ( 2039837875)
  • In this case the key is 10 digit decimal   ( 2039837875)
  • Fill the fields below: your email , your Key
  • After this, click on the Send button to send at us the information
  • Then, after sending the necessary information, proceed with payment at Buy Now With PayPal.
  • After payment processing, your master password will be sent immediately (to your email and PayPal email address)
  • After you receive the password turn off and ON again laptop and put your password

Price for unlock 1 unit Acer 10 digits password is: $14.00

If you have an Acer, Gateway, PackardBell 8 decimal digits example 74003099, we will give you the possibility for you to remove the password from  BIOS

  • Power on your laptop and wait for the password screen
  • Enter the wrong password three times
  • You will receive System disabled code from which the password can be calculated.

  • Please Type your Key  example see picture (74003099)
  • In this case, Key key is 8 digit hexadecimal   ( 74003099)
  • Fill the fields below: your email , your key
  • After this, click on the Send button to send at us the information
  • Then, after sending the necessary information, proceed with payment at Buy Now With PayPal.
  • After payment processing, your master password will be sent immediately (to your email and PayPal email address)
  • After you receive the password turn off and ON again laptop and put your password

  • Price for unlock 1 unit Acer 8 Digit key  is:  $6.00

title.rendered: How to unlock Sony Vaio bios Password

content.rendered:
How to unlock Sony Vaio One-time bios Password

If you have a Sony Vaio 16 characters 4×4 we will give you the possibility for you to remove the password from  BIOS

  • Power on your laptop and wait for the password screen
  • Enter the wrong password three times
  • You will see a screen with KEY (xxxx–xxxx–xxxx–xxxx) and you will be asked for enter ONETIME PASSWORD.

  • Please Type your KEY  example see picture below (16 chars KEY e.g. V29F-R8TJ-DKX3-878K)

  • In this case, System Disable key is 16 chars KEY  V29F-R8TJ-DKX3-878K
  • Fill the fields below: your email, your KEY. After this, click on the Send button to send at us the information
  • Then, after sending the necessary information, proceed with payment at Buy Now With PayPal.
  • After payment processing, your master password will be sent immediately (to your email and PayPal email address)
  • In Laptop: enter a calculated password, then push Enter key.

VERY IMPORTANT: Do not power off the computer once you provide us with a KEY (Key: xxxx–xxxx–xxxx–xxxx), wait for a one-time password. There’s a unique password for every KEY.Don’t turn off your notebook, don’t restart it, don’t enter anything except generated code.

Price for unlock 1 unit Sony One-time password is:    $ 12.00

How to unlock Sony Vaio with 7 digits serial number

If you have a Sony Vaio 7 digit serial number example ( 4494333 ) we will give you the possibility for you to remove the password from  BIOS

  • Power on your laptop and wait for the password screen

  • In this case, serial number is 4494333
  • Fill the fields below: your email , your KEY.
  • After this, click on the Send button to send at us the information
  • Then, after sending the necessary information, proceed with payment at Buy Now With PayPal.
  • After payment processing, your master password will be sent immediately (to your email and PayPal email address)
  • In Laptop: enter a calculated password, then push Enter key.

VERY IMPORTANT: Do not power off the computer once you provide us with a KEY (Key: xxxx–xxxx–xxxx–xxxx), wait for a one-time password. There’s a unique password for every KEY.Don’t turn off your notebook, don’t restart it, don’t enter anything except generated code.

title.rendered: How to unlock Fujitsu-Siemens bios Password

content.rendered:
How to unlock Fujitsu-Siemens bios Password

If you have a Fujitsu Siemens 5 Decimal digits example 07437, we will give you the possibility for you to remove the password from  BIOS

  • Power on your laptop and wait for the password screen
  • Enter the wrong password three times
  • You will receive System disabled code from which the password can be calculated.

  • Please Type your System Disabled  example see picture ( 07437)
  • In this case, System Disabled key is 5 digit decimal   ( 07437)
  • Fill the fields below: your email , your System Disabled
  • After this, click on the Send button to send at us the information
  • Then, after sending the necessary information, proceed with payment at Buy Now With PayPal.
  • After payment processing, your master password will be sent immediately (to your email and PayPal email address)
  • After you receive the password turn off and ON again laptop and put your password

Price for unlock 1 unit Fujitsu 5 Decimal digits password is:    $ 6.00

If you have a Fujitsu Siemens 8 hexadecimal digits example PEA1BE6F, we will give you the possibility for you to remove the password from  BIOS

  • Power on your laptop and wait for the password screen
  • Enter the wrong password three times
  • You will receive System disabled code from which the password can be calculated.

  • Please Type your System Disabled  example see picture (PEA1BE6F)
  • In this case, System Disabled key is 8 digit hexadecimal   ( PEA1BE6F)
